{"id": "1275368393498820641", "channel_id": "1275368393498820641", "type": 0, "author_id": "1226317601831911467", "author_name": "tranquil_monkey_73179", "author_bot": false, "content": "队伍前三号为混沌，四号位是血肉/深海/超维界域时，借用角色会借不到另外两个界域。\n\n\n但是，四号位本来就是要被其他界域的角色替代了，那就没必要在判断逻辑中把四号位的界域包含起来。\n\n我知道界域不能混编，但是这个判断逻辑也可以优化一下吧？或者更简单点，直接给一个弹窗提示玩家不能混编，而不是现在这样直接显示为空。", "timestamp": "2024-08-20T08:18:40.209000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1275368393872248854", "filename": "studio_video_1724141479098.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 2652738, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1275368393498820641/1275368393872248854/studio_video_1724141479098.mp4?ex=6a003f60&is=69feede0&hm=8e9dcc7c2a3ed6ac80c34986697eca224ff1d6360ec863ffb653a0cef8b6a26d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1275368393498820641", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "能不能优化一下队伍借用角色的判断逻辑", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
